James Foye III, ónyé a maara nke ọma dị ka KEYZBABY, bụ ónyé America na-emepụta ihe ndekọ, onye na-ede egwu, onye injinia ọdịyo na onye injinịa ndekọ si Buffalo, New York. Ọ bụ otu ọkara nké The Upperclassmen, otu mmepụta na Ayo the Producer
KEYZBABY esorowo ndị na-ese ihe dịka Chris Brown, Bryson Tiller, K Michelle, Wiz Khalifa, Diddy na Rick Ross rụọ ọrụ.
